title: Millikin grad wins raves as Chicago co-star in "The Producers" (Millikin University)
text: ( Source : Millikin University ) Millikin University graduate Cara Chumbley '12 recently wrapped up a month-long run as the female lead in the hit musical ' The Producers .' The production was held at Stage 773, a performance venue in Chicago
